org.opendaylight.controller.config.yangjmxgenerator

Class ServiceInterfaceEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.config.yangjmxgenerator.AbstractEntry
      • org.opendaylight.controller.config.yangjmxgenerator.ServiceInterfaceEntry

  • public class ServiceInterfaceEntry
extends AbstractEntry
    Represents identity derived from ConfigConstants.SERVICE_TYPE_Q_NAME. Example: 

      identity eventbus {
  description
  "Service representing an event bus. The service acts as message
  router between event producers and event consumers";

  base "config:service-type";
  config:java-class "com.google.common.eventbus.EventBus";
  }
